title: Lake Chelan National Recreation Area: Photo Gallery
body: Explore This Park    Learn About the Park     Photos & Multimedia     Photo Gallery              Photo Gallery                    Areas of North Cascades National Park Service Complex   5 Photos  Discover the North Cascades landscapes which make up the amazing scenery.           Best of the North Cascades   13 Photos  A visual overview of North Cascades highlights. Come be inspired by these mountains.          Alpine Adaptation   3 Photos  Some of the flora and fauna adapted to life in the subalpine and alpine zones around Cascade Pass.            Rivers to Peaks: A Journey Along the Trails  of the North Cascades   5 Photos  Tour some of the most remote (and some not so remote!) corners of the greater North Cascades with outdoor photographer Andy Porter.           Park Trails   21 Photos  Photos from trails in the North Cascades National Park, Ross Lake and Lake Chelan National Recreation Areas.
